28:
WITH EnrollmentDifference AS (
    SELECT 
        "School Name", 
        "DOCType", 
        "Enrollment (K-12)" - "Enrollment (Ages 5-17)" AS enrollment_diff
    FROM frpm
    JOIN schools ON frpm."CDSCode" = schools."CDSCode"
    WHERE "Charter Funding Type" = 'Locally funded'
),
AverageDifference AS (
    SELECT AVG(enrollment_diff) AS avg_diff
    FROM EnrollmentDifference
)
SELECT 
    "School Name", 
    "DOCType"
FROM EnrollmentDifference
WHERE enrollment_diff > (SELECT avg_diff FROM AverageDifference);	----- bird -----	california_schools

FROM satscores ss
JOIN (
    SELECT cds, (COALESCE("AvgScrRead", 0) + COALESCE("AvgScrMath", 0) + COALESCE("AvgScrWrite", 0)) / 3 AS avg_score

) AS subquery ON ss.cds = subquery.cds
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY subquery.avg_score ASC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
